{"type": "article", "id": 27292, "title": "烈酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-25T06:32:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702124656IQi0bPXvjT2RFNfx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>看腻了大红大金的烈酒包装？<a href=\"http://colateralmkt.com/\">Colateral Advanced Marketing</a> 的设计师们带来了一个另辟蹊径的创意：通过海洋元素来表现一款墨西哥的梅斯卡尔酒（mezcal，是龙舌兰酒的一种）El Golfo de México。印有小船锚的木塞封住了纤细透明的瓶身，采用蓝黑配色在包装上印上了海底以及抽着烟斗的大胡子水手的图像，带给人一种清新明亮的感觉。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124654uK6NzP8QL2y9lqJp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124655JOHMcXQxA2gPG5Zb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124655WdjgZlY3rXVTDxFS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}